		<title>wordpress修改固定链接</title>
		<link>http://10.211.55.4:8080/wordpress/5</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 20 Oct 2020 14:17:08 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[qzhang]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://10.211.55.4:8080/wordpress/?p=5</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>问题描述：修改固定链接后，访问文章时出现404错误</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>1、在wordpress的根目录下现在.htaccess,并修改权限为777</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>cd /var/www/html/wordpress
vi .htaccess
chmod 777 .htaccess</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>2、在wordpress管理后台修改固定链接的格式</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>自定义结构：http://10.10.10.1:8080/wordpress/%post_id%</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>点击保存</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":9,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="http://10.211.55.4:8080/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/截屏2020-10-20-下午10.20.04.png" alt="" class="wp-image-9"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>3、修改https.conf文件</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>vi vi /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf
添加
LoadModule rewrite_module modules/mod_rewrite.so
&lt;Directory "/var/www/html">
    Options Indexes FollowSymLinks
    #原来默认AllowOverride None 修改成  AllowOverride All
    AllowOverride All
    Require all granted
&lt;/Directory></code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>4、重启httpd服务</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>systemctl restart http</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
